paths:
  "/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourcegroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Storage.Admin/farms/{farmId}/blobservices/{serviceType}":
    get:
      description: Returns the BLOB service.
      operationId: BlobServices_Get
      parameters:
        - description: Subscription Id.
          in: path
          name: subscriptionId
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns the BLOB service.:
              value: 9ad61516-995c-4873-a21f-7e44904f0ed2
        - description: Resource group name.
          in: path
          name: resourceGroupName
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns the BLOB service.:
              value: System.local
        - description: Farm Id.
          in: path
          name: farmId
          required: true
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns the BLOB service.:
              value: 3cf03497-c44a-4e51-a56f-3987d88c70af
        - description: The service type.
          in: path
          name: serviceType
          required: true
          x-ms-enum:
            modelAsString: true
            name: ServiceType
          x-ms-parameter-location: method
          schema:
            type: string
            enum:
              - default
          examples:
            Returns the BLOB service.:
              value: default
        - description: REST Api Version.
          in: query
          name: api-version
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          examples:
            Returns the BLOB service.:
              value: 2015-12-01-preview
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK -- The BLOB service has been returned.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/BlobService"
              examples:
                Returns the BLOB service.:
                  $ref: "#/components/examples/Returns_the_BLOB_service."
        "404":
          description: NOT FOUND -- The specified farm was not found.
      tags:
        - BlobServices
